data.description: Transform this 2000 square foot stately all brick 2 story, 4 bedroom home into the house you've dreamed of! This stunning corner lot and home offers large concrete wrap around patio with brick fencing and   the perfect grounds for flower beds, gardens and play areas! Large front brick concrete porch welcomes you into a traditional floor plan with Living Room, dining room, kitchen with breakfast area, family room with brick fireplace, and powder room. The second story has 4 generous size bedrooms with double closets plus 1 full and 1 half bath ( that can be reconverted to a full bathroom.) Primary suite has access to a balcony overlooking the yard! Lower level has playroom/den, laundry room, and access to garages and driveway with parking for 4 additional autos. Home does need work, is being sold AS IS.Location, curb appeal and space makes this a great find!  A/C and some flooring new in 2022. Convenient to schools, parks and shopping.PRICED TO SELL!
